<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>URL Shortener</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:opsz,wght@9..40,300;9..40,400;9..40,500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/landing.css" />
  <style>
    footer span { color: var(--muted2); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="logo">Shortne<span class="logo-accent">r</span></div>
  <div class="nav-actions">
    <a href="/user/login" class="btn-ghost">Log in</a>
    <a href="/user/signup" class="btn-primary">Get started free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-badge">
    <div class="badge-dot"></div>
    Free URL shortener with click tracking
  </div>
  <h1>Short links,<br><em>real results.</em></h1>
  <p>Shorten any URL in seconds. Track every click and manage all your links in one place.</p>

  <div class="demo-box">
    <input class="demo-input" type="text" value="https://example.com/some/very/long/url/nobody-wants-to-share" readonly />
    <button class="demo-btn">Shorten →</button>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="stats">
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-num">10k+</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Links shortened</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-num">99%</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Uptime</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-num">0ms</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Redirect delay</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="features" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
  <div class="feature">
    <div class="feature-icon icon-purple">⚡</div>
    <h3>Instant shortening</h3>
    <p>Paste your URL and get a short link immediately. No setup, no waiting.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="feature">
    <div class="feature-icon icon-red">📊</div>
    <h3>Click tracking</h3>
    <p>See exactly how many times each link has been clicked, updated in real time.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="feature">
    <div class="feature-icon icon-green">🔐</div>
    <h3>Private & secure</h3>
    <p>Your links are tied to your account. Nobody else can see or manage them.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="how">
  <p class="section-label">How it works</p>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-bar bar-purple"></div>
      <div class="step-num">01</div>
      <h3>Create an account</h3>
      <p>Sign up free in seconds. No credit card, no nonsense.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-bar bar-red"></div>
      <div class="step-num">02</div>
      <h3>Paste your URL</h3>
      <p>Drop in any long link and hit generate. Done in one click.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-bar bar-mixed"></div>
      <div class="step-num">03</div>
      <h3>Share & track</h3>
      <p>Share your short link anywhere and watch the clicks come in.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="preview-section">
  <div class="preview-text">
    <h2>All your links,<br><em>one place.</em></h2>
    <p>A clean dashboard to manage every link you've created. Click counts at a glance, original URLs always accessible.</p>
    <a href="/user/signup" class="btn-primary" style="display:inline-block; text-decoration:none;">Start for free →</a>
  </div>
  <div class="preview-card">
    <div class="preview-card-header">
      <div class="dot dot-r"></div>
      <div class="dot dot-y"></div>
      <div class="dot dot-g"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="preview-card-body">
      <div class="url-row">
        <div class="url-left">
          <span class="url-short">trimr.app/x9k2m</span>
          <span class="url-original">https://github.com/user/project-repo</span>
        </div>
        <span class="url-clicks">142 clicks</span>
      </div>
      <div class="url-row">
        <div class="url-left">
          <span class="url-short">trimr.app/p3jqw</span>
          <span class="url-original">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/long</span>
        </div>
        <span class="url-clicks">87 clicks</span>
      </div>
      <div class="url-row">
        <div class="url-left">
          <span class="url-short">trimr.app/t7bnx</span>
          <span class="url-original">https://youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ</span>
        </div>
        <span class="url-clicks">34 clicks</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="cta">
  <h2>Ready to start<br><em>trimming?</em></h2>
  <p>Free forever. No credit card needed.</p>
  <a href="/user/signup" class="btn-white">Create free account →</a>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>Built with <span>Express + MongoDB</span> · © 2025 Trimr</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>